CircleRadius: max distance of path between point and context
PointOnCircleSpacingMethod: how we are choosing where the points are in the circle
SpaceBetween: items will be generated on a circle this much apart
NumberOfPoints: this many items will be generated on a circle
ArcDirection: If you generate items on a piece of circle you define direction of Arc cut here
ArcAngle: If you generate items on a piece of circle you define angle of Arc cut here
bIgnoreAnyContextActorsWhenGeneratingCir: ignore tracing into context actors when generating the circle
